{
  "stem": "1169.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We stayed here for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We slept on straw, but it was warm at least.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then they took us to French Switzerland, near a city called Montreux.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we stayed in various hotels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They assigned hotels on the mountains above Montreux.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We want to a place called Caux, to a place called Lausanne to place called Chamby.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The Swiss were not too happy we are there-- that we were there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They really didn't like us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they wanted to get rid of us but fast.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they said that they want to send us to Uganda.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But this time, you know, we already learned our lesson a little bit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we said, nothing doing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We are not going to Uganda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You cannot do this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We said, if the Swiss want to send us to Uganda, there's only one way they can do it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Everyone on that day is going to stay in his bed, in pajamas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they'll have to take every Jew on a stretcher and put him on a train, and send him to Uganda.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There's no-- and we are going to invite the newspapers, also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they changed their mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to the very last day, they did not give us any freedom of movement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We need a permit to leave, to come and go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were like semi-incarcerated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews, the local Jews, I'm sorry, but they were not much better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hardly anyone came to visit us, to see us, to befriend us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a rabbi in Montreux who possibly visited us once or twice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name is Rabbi [?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
